author: Aila Slisco
title: Georgia and Mississippi Governors Issue Shelter-In-Place Orders Amid Coronavirus Pandemic
description: Residents of Georgia and Mississippi are expected on Friday to join millions of others across the U.S. under orders to stay at home to help stem the spread of COVID-19.
